divs: sighting detailswe were driving south\west on hwy 156 from santa ynez,ca towards santa barbara, ca. we noticed lights in the sky as it is very dark with no business or residential in the area. we saw five light sources, that were some what circular in shape. the circled around each other while moving left to right in the sky.the entire group of lights moved individually but at the same time moved in unison left to right in the horizon. then all lights became one and disapeared at once.
